FBIS3-15956 "drsov048_a_94004" FBIS-SOV-94-048 Document Type:Daily Report 11 Mar 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Zhirinovskiy Declines Invitation To Meet Nixon LD1003183394 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 1736 GMT 10 Mar 94 LD1003183394 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [By ITAR-TASS correspondent Igor Belskiy] [Excerpt] Moscow, 10 Mar -- Vladimir Zhironvskiy, chairman of the Liberal Democratic Party [LDP], has today said he does not want to meet with former U.S. President Richard Nixon, the ITAR-TASS correspondent was told by the LDP press service at the end of the State Duma faction sitting. [passage omitted]
